n<br />\n中共用過咩方法搞連登，我地統計下<br />\nDDOS fail<br />\n扮最勇同最和理非拉罵戰，成功過一段短時間<br />\n失敗主義撚，搞親遊行都話冇人，日輸夜輸，都有啲用<br />\n<br />\n可能仲威嚇過連仔同禁連登，不過冇嘢發生就唔講<br />\n<br />\n而家就派人搞爛連登，瘋狂開廢post，屌人送頭，情緒勒索，濫情罐頭式回覆<br />\n務求令人對連登厭倦<br />\n再配合有人嗌連登已死，唔好上咁多，放棄佢啦<br />\n<br />\n一個重要抗爭號召平台就搞廢左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T02:05:54.000Z","msg":"希望大家回歸初心 當初係為咩出嚟<br />\n<br />\n過程有幾多義士犧牲 我哋放棄對得住佢哋咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家唔好睇小自己嘅能力 做到幾多得幾多<br />\n<br />\n可以失望 不能絕望<br />\n就算情況幾壞 我哋香港人繼續努力 好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bca5cd0ea0bba848f353ef4fc828130d1282679","tid":2072833,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ade356a4d1b565180957d7435f4921308006e96e","tid":2072833,"uid":216907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T01:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T02:06:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c8d3f34f56ae1be5782521f0f6ce826808aa67e","tid":2072833,"uid":69473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T02:06:10.000Z","msg":"push 兄弟爬山"},{"pid":"db7c264b7bced7e54af3fcff402ac105982a77f7","tid":2072833,"uid":302831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T02:06:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0bd209c41cdedb